usda to reduc citru estim program the u.s. agricultur depart ' nation agricultur statist servic ( nass ) said it will chang it citru estim program for california and arizona , start in 1988. nass said it will discontinu california forecast for lemon dure decemb , februari , march , may and june and for grapefruit and tangerin for those month plu novemb . forecast for lemon will be issu in octob , novemb , januari , april and juli and for grapefruit in octob , januari , april , and juli and for tangerin in octob , januari and april . there will be no chang in the estim program for california orang . arizona forecast will be drop for lemon , orang , grapefruit and tangerin in novemb , decemb februari , march , may and june , with forecast retain in octob , januari , april and juli , it said . there will be no chang in the estim program for citru in texa or florida .